article.description: — Justin Webster had 20 points as Hawaii topped Cal Poly 84-68 on Friday night.
article.headline: Webster scores 20 to lead Hawaii past Cal Poly 84-68
article.linkText: Webster scores 20 to lead Hawaii past Cal Poly 84-68
article.story: HONOLULU -- — Justin Webster had 20 points as Hawaii topped Cal Poly 84-68 on Friday night. Mate Colina had 14 points and nine rebounds for Hawaii (6-5, 4-5 Big West Conference). Casdon Jardine added 14 points. Junior Madut had 13 points. Hawaii totaled 41 points in the first half, a season high for the team. Colby Rogers had 15 points for the Mustangs (3-12, 1-8). Alimamy Koroma added 14 points. Mark Crowe had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
